Posts.Title: Cancer

Posts.Content: We were all scared but no matter what it is you need to find out and deal with it. It is what it is whether you wait to find out or not. Waiting is not going to change that. The odds are that it is nothing serious but if it is something to worry about it is better to find out sooner than later and begin treatment...time is on your side if you don't wait. Keep your chin up and come out fighting. Good Luck.
